{
  "texts": [
    "The scientist's expertise, intuition, and understanding of the field are crucial in guiding the AI, ensuring that the generated content is relevant, accurate, and meaningful.",
    "This interaction creates a symbiotic relationship where both the AI and the scientist contribute to the final scientific output.",
    "Furthermore, this structural coupling leads us to another structural coupling between technology and science, where authorship as a form interacts with technology, integrating it into the scientific field of inquiry.",
    "Authorship, traditionally viewed as the domain of human intellect and creativity, now encompasses the collaborative inputs from advanced technologies.",
    "This integration is not seamless or straightforward; it involves a continuous negotiation of roles and boundaries."
  ]
}